#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: french-typo.php:707
msgid "French Typo"
msgstr "French Typo"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
msgid "https://github.com/jaz-on/french-typo"
msgstr "https://github.com/jaz-on/french-typo"

#. Description of the plugin
msgid "Automatically applies French typography rules to your content: non-breaking spaces before punctuation marks (; : ! ? % « ») and special character replacements ((c) → ©, (r) → ®, (tm)/(TM) → ™)."
msgstr "Applique automatiquement les règles de typographie française à votre contenu : espaces insécables avant la ponctuation (; : ! ? % « ») et remplacement des caractères spéciaux ((c) → ©, (r) → ®, (tm)/(TM) → ™)."

#. Author of the plugin
msgid "Jason Rouet"
msgstr "Jason Rouet"

#. Author URI of the plugin
msgid "https://profiles.wordpress.org/jaz_on/"
msgstr "https://profiles.wordpress.org/jaz_on/"

#: french-typo.php:706
msgid "French Typo Settings"
msgstr "Réglages French Typo"

#: french-typo.php:750
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Réglages"

#: french-typo.php:766
#: french-typo.php:1189
msgid "Non-breaking spaces"
msgstr "Espaces insécables"

#: french-typo.php:772
#: french-typo.php:786
msgid "Automatic replacement"
msgstr "Remplacement automatique"

#: french-typo.php:780
#: french-typo.php:1195
msgid "Special characters"
msgstr "Caractères spéciaux"

#: french-typo.php:794
#: french-typo.php:1202
msgid "Posts and pages"
msgstr "Articles et pages"

#: french-typo.php:800
msgid "Apply to"
msgstr "Appliquer à"

#: french-typo.php:808
#: french-typo.php:1208
msgid "Advanced options"
msgstr "Options avancées"

#: french-typo.php:814
msgid "Additional content"
msgstr "Contenu supplémentaire"

#. translators: %1$s and %2$s are URL attributes (escaped). %3$s is a list of punctuation characters.
#: french-typo.php:833
msgid "This plugin automatically handles <a href=\"%1$s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">non-breaking spaces</a> or <a href=\"%2$s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">thin non-breaking spaces</a> for the characters %3$s."
msgstr "Cette extension gère automatiquement les <a href=\"%1$s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">espaces insécables</a> ou les <a href=\"%2$s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">espaces insécables fines</a> pour les caractères %3$s."

#. translators: %1$s–%5$s are lowercase HTML tag names (script, style, pre, code, textarea).
#: french-typo.php:846
msgid "Narrow spaces are <strong>not</strong> inserted inside raw markup: <%1$s>, <%2$s>, nested <%3$s>/<%4$s>, and <%5$s>. Gutenberg Verse (<code>pre</code> with <code>wp-block-verse</code>) is still typographed unless <code>wp-block-code</code> is on the same <code>pre</code>."
msgstr "Les espaces insécables <strong>ne sont pas</strong> insérées dans le balisage brut : <%1$s>, <%2$s>, <%3$s> / <%4$s> imbriqués et <%5$s>. Le bloc Vers Gutenberg (<code>pre</code> avec <code>wp-block-verse</code>) reste typographié sauf si <code>wp-block-code</code> est sur le même <code>pre</code>."

#: french-typo.php:870
msgid "Disable"
msgstr "Désactiver"

#. translators: %s are both HTML entity codes
#: french-typo.php:877
msgid "Enable and use regular non-breaking spaces (HTML entity %1$s or %2$s)"
msgstr "Activer et utiliser les espaces insécables classiques (entité HTML %1$s ou %2$s)"

#. translators: %s is an HTML entity code
#: french-typo.php:888
msgid "Enable and use thin non-breaking spaces (HTML entity %s)"
msgstr "Activer et utiliser les espaces insécables fines (entité HTML %s)"

#: french-typo.php:895
msgid "Non-breaking spaces stay off until you pick regular or thin above and save your settings at least once (or they remain off if you keep disabling this feature)."
msgstr "Les espaces insécables restent désactivées tant que vous n’avez pas choisi ci-dessus l’une des options classique ou fine et enregistré vos réglages au moins une fois (elles restent aussi désactivées si vous laissez « Désactiver »)."

#: french-typo.php:898
msgid "Note: The thin non-breaking space may not display correctly. This depends on the font, browser version, and operating system used."
msgstr "Remarque : l’espace insécable fine peut ne pas s’afficher correctement selon la police, la version du navigateur et le système d’exploitation."

#. translators: %1$s–%7$s are character or entity codes shown in the settings UI
#: french-typo.php:915
msgid "Replaces %1$s with %2$s, %3$s with %4$s, and %5$s or %6$s with %7$s."
msgstr "Remplace %1$s par %2$s, %3$s par %4$s, et %5$s ou %6$s par %7$s."

#. translators: %1$s–%5$s are lowercase HTML tag names (script, style, pre, code, textarea).
#: french-typo.php:932
msgid "These replacements use the same raw-markup rules as narrow spaces: they do not run inside <%1$s>, <%2$s>, nested <%3$s>/<%4$s>, or <%5$s>."
msgstr "Ces remplacements suivent les mêmes règles de balisage brut que les espaces insécables : ils ne s’appliquent pas à l’intérieur de <%1$s>, <%2$s>, <%3$s> / <%4$s> imbriqués ni de <%5$s>."

#: french-typo.php:956
msgid "Replace special characters"
msgstr "Remplacer les caractères spéciaux"

#: french-typo.php:1015
msgid "Turn typography on or off for post and page titles and main content. Excerpts and all other areas are controlled under advanced options below."
msgstr "Activez ou désactivez la typographie pour les titres et le contenu principal des articles et des pages. Les extraits et les autres zones se règlent dans les options avancées ci-dessous."

#: french-typo.php:1026
msgid "Typography rules also apply to many other areas: widgets, menus, excerpts, custom fields, taxonomies, archives, comments, RSS feeds, REST API, user profiles, and breadcrumbs."
msgstr "La typographie peut aussi s’appliquer aux widgets, menus, extraits, champs personnalisés, taxonomies, archives, commentaires, flux RSS, API REST, profils utilisateurs et fil d’Ariane."

#: french-typo.php:1027
msgid "RSS feeds only run typography when RSS is enabled plus the matching area: titles (RSS + titles), full content (RSS + post content), excerpts (RSS + excerpts), comments (RSS + comments). REST API responses require REST API enabled plus titles/content/excerpts as appropriate for each field."
msgstr "Les flux RSS ne typographient que si l’option RSS est activée ainsi que la zone concernée : titres (RSS + titres), contenu (RSS + contenu d’article), extraits (RSS + extraits), commentaires (RSS + commentaires). Les réponses de l’API REST exigent l’option API REST ainsi que titres / contenu / extraits selon chaque champ."

#: french-typo.php:1028
msgid "Meta descriptions and social tags (Open Graph, Twitter Cards) from SEO plugins (Yoast SEO, Rank Math, SEOPress) are processed automatically when those integrations are enabled."
msgstr "Les méta-descriptions et balises sociales (Open Graph, Twitter Cards) des extensions SEO (Yoast SEO, Rank Math, SEOPress) sont traitées automatiquement lorsque ces intégrations sont actives."

#. translators: %s is a code example.
#: french-typo.php:1034
msgid "You can process custom text in PHP with the filter %s."
msgstr "Vous pouvez traiter du texte personnalisé en PHP avec le filtre %s."

#: french-typo.php:1052
msgid "Toggle advanced options visibility"
msgstr "Afficher ou masquer les options avancées"

#: french-typo.php:1053
msgid "Show advanced options"
msgstr "Afficher les options avancées"

#: french-typo.php:1058
msgid "Core WordPress Areas"
msgstr "Zones WordPress principales"

#: french-typo.php:1062
msgid "Excerpts"
msgstr "Extraits"

#: french-typo.php:1066
msgid "Widgets (text widgets and widget titles)"
msgstr "Widgets (contenu et titres des widgets texte)"

#: french-typo.php:1070
msgid "Menu items"
msgstr "Éléments de menu"

#: french-typo.php:1074
msgid "Archives (titles and descriptions)"
msgstr "Archives (titres et descriptions)"

#: french-typo.php:1078
msgid "Comment text and author names"
msgstr "Texte des commentaires et noms d’auteurs"

#: french-typo.php:1082
msgid "User profiles (descriptions)"
msgstr "Profils utilisateurs (descriptions)"

#: french-typo.php:1089
msgid "Custom Content"
msgstr "Contenu personnalisé"

#: french-typo.php:1093
msgid "Custom fields (ACF, Meta Box, etc.)"
msgstr "Champs personnalisés (ACF, Meta Box, etc.)"

#: french-typo.php:1097
msgid "Taxonomies (categories, tags, custom taxonomies)"
msgstr "Taxonomies (catégories, étiquettes, taxonomies personnalisées)"

#: french-typo.php:1104
msgid "Integrations"
msgstr "Intégrations"

#: french-typo.php:1108
msgid "RSS feeds"
msgstr "Flux RSS"

#: french-typo.php:1112
msgid "REST API responses"
msgstr "Réponses de l’API REST"

#: french-typo.php:1116
msgid "Breadcrumbs (Yoast, Rank Math, SEOPress)"
msgstr "Fil d’Ariane (Yoast, Rank Math, SEOPress)"

#: french-typo.php:1122
msgid "By default, all additional content areas are processed."
msgstr "Par défaut, toutes ces zones supplémentaires sont traitées."

#: french-typo.php:1140
msgid "Post and page titles"
msgstr "Titres des articles et des pages"

#: french-typo.php:1144
msgid "Post and page content"
msgstr "Contenu des articles et des pages"

#: french-typo.php:1148
msgid "By default, both titles and content are processed. Use advanced options for excerpts and other areas."
msgstr "Par défaut, les titres et le contenu sont traités. Utilisez les options avancées pour les extraits et les autres zones."

#: french-typo.php:1165
msgid "Thank you for using this plugin"
msgstr "Merci d’utiliser cette extension"

#: french-typo.php:1167
msgid "This plugin automatically applies French typography rules to your WordPress content: non-breaking spaces before punctuation marks and special character replacements. Configure the options below according to your needs."
msgstr "Cette extension applique automatiquement les règles de typographie française à votre contenu WordPress : espaces insécables avant la ponctuation et remplacements de caractères spéciaux. Configurez les options ci-dessous selon vos besoins."

#. translators: %1$s is a link to GitHub, %2$s is a link to Ko-fi
#: french-typo.php:1174
msgid "Find the source code on %1$s. If this plugin is useful to you, you can support its author and help make further developments on %2$s."
msgstr "Le code source est sur %1$s. Si cette extension vous est utile, vous pouvez soutenir son auteur et les développements futurs sur %2$s."

#. translators: %s is the version number
#: french-typo.php:1223
msgid "Installed version: %s"
msgstr "Version installée : %s"
